  <div class="headline-block">
    <tegaki-renderer class="tegaki-headline" font="Caveat" speed="2.0">The Operator Who Learned to Build the Machine</tegaki-renderer>
    <p class="headline-deck">After 13 years scaling hyper-growth tech companies from the inside — DigitalOcean, KeepTruckin, Cloudways — Saad Farooq now builds the communication and orchestration layer between AI agents and the real world. Not demos. Production systems that run 24/7.</p>
